text: Out to Sea is a 1997 American romantic comedy movie directed by Martha Coolidge and starring Jack Lemmon, Walter Matthau, Dyan Cannon, Gloria DeHaven, Donald O'Connor, Rue McClanahan, Edward Mulhare, Estelle Harris. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * Category:1997 romantic comedy movies Category:American romantic comedy movies Category:20th Century Fox movies Category:Movies directed by Martha Coolidge Category:Movies about old age Category:Movies set in Mexico
